Panthers – Online Library Management System

Team Name: Panthers

Team Members:
- Isaac Vunzi
- Brian Tramuel
- Sam Suther
- Will Armentrout
- Sana Ullah

Project Description:
This project involves developing an online library management system with an
integrated database to track books, user accounts, and library transactions.
The system manages book availability, associates borrowed books with user
accounts, records checkout and return dates, and supports the full borrowing
and return workflow.

